///     2,  7,  6,  4,  9
///   Sum the last:
///     2 + 7 + 6 + 4 + 9 = 28 = s2
/// <br>
/// s1 + s2 = 70 which ends in zero which means that 49927398716 passes the Luhn test</pre>
